peopleAlsoAsk.question: What year did the Beautiful Crissy doll come out?
peopleAlsoAsk.snippet: After the New York Toy Fair in 1969, Ideal's "Beautiful Crissy" was released to the buying public. Each production year enjoyed some new variations. Production runs of the Crissy doll early in 1969 had adjustable hair that "grew" down to the doll's feet.
